We'd like to introduce you to <b>Duke</b>, our featured citizen of the week!<br><br>Duke has been living happily at his <a href="http://millsberry.com/home/?user=fatdog2468"><a href='/home/?user=fatdog2468'>59748-C Breeze Street</a> home in Golden Valley</a> since October 10th, 2008. Since he's lived here, Duke has come to love Millsberry and all of the sunny days in Golden Valley. <br><br>Duke describes himself as very shy, a little friendly, and caring. If you ever want to strike up a conversation, we'll give you a hint: his interests are animals, animals, and more animals. There's nothing wrong with knowing what you like. <br><br>Duke has been busy since he moved to Millsberry. In the little over a month, he's managed to rack up trophies for Kai's Surfari, 'Hop 'n' Drop', Sink Three, and Home Run Derby. <br><br>If you're looking for Duke, your best bet is to check the Football Game, the Movie Theater, or the Pizza Place. When he's not kicking it at these hangouts, he's probably listening to some of his favorite tunes: Classic Rock, Country, and Jazz. <br><br>Next time you see Duke, give him a high-five and congratulate him for being such an outstanding citizen!<br></div>
